{"tid":990764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港23歲女僕被捕","createTime":"2019-01-22T01:08:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T13:20:43.000Z","uid":2104,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8e6243348aeed39e9c071cebc365e5364f249830","tid":990764,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sVbi6b7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsVbi6b7.png&h=60c299e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n赴台灣旅遊的廿三歲譚姓香港女子，周日涉嫌在桃園中壢地區一間女僕咖啡店打工，遭移民署人員帶署調查。譚辯稱不懂法例，惟當局將依例強制遣送她出境及管制入境，店主亦將被罰款。<br />\n<br />\n當地首宗 辯稱不知違法<br />\n<br />\n綽號「鈴鈴」的譚女，是熱衷於扮演學生及女僕的Cosplayer（角色扮演愛好者），Facebook專頁有上萬粉絲。據悉譚女持入台證多次以觀光名義，到全台各地多間咖啡店打工。譚女更在網上公告周知，加上店家宣傳，當局因而接獲舉報。移民署於周日突襲稽查，查獲譚女本人。據悉，譚自稱來台是與網上認識的女僕同好人士交流，否認有利益關係，不清楚會違法。<br />\n<br />\n移民署專勤隊表示，香港女子來台當女僕工作屬當地首宗。涉嫌違反《就業服務法》的女僕咖啡店負責人，將面臨最高七十五萬元新台幣（約十九萬三千港元）罰款。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"263334978b72fc77254eb29a4b516fa75c8eed9f","tid":990764,"uid":220431,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:09:43.000Z","msg":"想差電"},{"pid":"094fba0a548ed44fe45825796f244b759313cfc3","tid":990764,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:14:10.000Z","msg":"送去男監倉幾日啦, 免罰款"},{"pid":"fe43ec52657ff1b6b0610a5b9dc3eeea0f2e3292","tid":990764,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:17:11.000Z","msg":"個鼻lone想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"919101b6775607142f6256336a3b9f54afdc81ca","tid":990764,"uid":139967,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T02:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/17o14my.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2